# Changelog
All notable changes to this project will be documented in this file.

The format is based on [Keep a Changelog](http://keepachangelog.com/en/1.0.0/)
and this project adheres to [Semantic Versioning](http://semver.org/spec/v2.0.0.html).

## Unreleased
	### Added

	### Changed


	### Removed


## [0.2.0]
	## Changed
	Replaced write(2) calls with send(2)
	Replaced read(2) calls with recv(2)
	In server mode, call yasock_set_socket_options for cli_sd in I/O routines

	## Added
	Version and Help options
	Automated generation of man page with help2man
	MSS (option -X): Let user specify a TCP MSS
	Half Close (option -h): Let client performs a shutdown when sent all data
	Linger option (option -L): Set SO_LINGER on socket
	Timeout send/recv: SO_RCVTIMEO (-x) and SO_SNDTIMEO (-y)

	## Removed


## [0.1.0] - 2018-04-20
	## Added
	Integration of Autotools
	Integration of Git

	### Changed
	Modified COPYING for applying GNU General Public License
	Modified INSTALL for supressing symbolic link

	## Removed


